high_descs: walk to the white table on the left
grab the cabbage on the table
open the refrigerator, put the cabbage in, wait a while, take the cabbage out
turn around to the white table
put the cabbage on the table

high_descs: Turn left and go to the table.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Turn left and left again to go to the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge for a little bit and take it back out.
Turn around and go back to the table.
Set the lettuce back onto the table.
anns.task_desc: Chill the lettuce and put it on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the white table.
Pick the lettuce up from the table.
Go left and then left again to face the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge and then shut the door and open the door and take the lettuce out and shut the door.
Go to the left and turn around to face the white table.
Put the lettuce on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce on the table.
